header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - SEMIFINAL

videos.description: North Carolina gathers in the tunnel before taking the court to faceoff with Duke in the ACC tournament semifinals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Tar Heels get hyped for matchup with Blue Devils) 2017/03/10 Shortstop OnScene

videos.headline: Tar Heels get hyped for matchup with Blue Devils

videos.description: UNC's Kennedy Meeks gets off to a hot start by taking the pass inside and making the layup against Duke.
videos.headline: UNC dominating in the paint early

videos.description: UNC's Joel Berry II drives to the basket and makes the and-1 layup in the first half against Duke.
videos.headline: UNC attacking the basket against Duke

videos.description: Grayson Allen makes three straight 3-pointers to help Duke keep it close against North Carolina.
videos.headline: Grayson Allen heating up from behind the arc

videos.description: Justin Jackson takes the pass and makes the jumper just outside of the paint to extend UNC's lead over Duke.
videos.headline: UNC's strong inside game continues

videos.description: UNC's Theo Pinson finds Isaiah Hicks in transition for the layup to extend the Tar Heels' lead over Duke.
videos.headline: UNC widens the gap with transition bucket

videos.description: Jayson Tatum goes coast-to-coast for the and-1 layup as Duke tries to keep things close against UNC.
videos.headline: Duke's Tatum completes 3-point play

videos.description: Justin Jackson nails the 3-pointer to extend North Carolina's lead over Duke.
videos.headline: UNC's Jackson connects from 3-point range

videos.description: Jayson Tatum drives and throws down the two-handed dunk as Duke tries to close the gap against UNC.
videos.headline: Tatum's dunk energizes Blue Devils

videos.description: Theo Pinson finds a cutting Isaiah Hicks for the easy dunk as UNC leads Duke.
videos.headline: UNC's Hicks left all alone for dunk

videos.description: Grayson Allen gets open in the corner and nails the 3-pointer as Duke keeps it close against UNC.
videos.headline: Duke gets back in it with 3-pointer

videos.description: Frank Jackson makes the 3-pointer before Luke Kennard drives for the bucket as Duke takes the lead over North Carolina.
videos.headline: Huge run gives Duke first lead of game

videos.description: Nate Britt drives for the and-1 layup as UNC continues to trade blows with Duke in the second half.
videos.headline: UNC not backing down from Duke

videos.description: Luke Kennard drills the corner 3-pointer before Harry Giles catches the lob from Grayson Allen for the alley-oop as Duke tries to pull away from UNC.
videos.headline: Duke puts up five quick points in style

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen finds Harry Giles in the paint for the wide-open dunk as the Blue Devils extend their lead over UNC.
videos.headline: Duke picks apart the defense for easy dunk

videos.description: Duke head coach, Mike Krzyzewski, talks about how his key players came alive to propel the Blue Devils over UNC in the ACC Tournament semifinal.
videos.headline: Coach K tears up after gutsy win over UNC

videos.description: No. 14 Duke outscores No. 6 North Carolina by 17 in the second half en route to a 93-83 victory to advance to the title game.
videos.headline: Duke storms past UNC in ACC semis
